  <name>Guitar Assistant</name>
  <summary>Minimal desktop assistant for guitar practice</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Guitar Assistant brings a tuner, metronome, smart chord notepad, and fretboard visualizer
      into one focused interface. Audio uses low-latency capture via PortAudio; the UI is built with PyQt6.
    </p>
